#ROOM
Vnum     33017
Name     &OValley of the Watchers&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Colossal stone statues of troll ancestors line this wide, sandy valley.
The wind whistling through the statues creates a low, moaning sound
that unnerves even the bravest explorers.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    33012
Desc      Waterspring Field.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    33018
Desc      The Noxious Lair.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 33007 1 33017
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     33018
Name     &OThe Noxious Lair&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The ground here is porous and covered in a strange, sticky resin.
Massive sinkholes lead into darkness. This is the territory of the
silithid bugs, and the buzzing is deafening.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    33017
Desc      Valley of the Watchers.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    33019
Desc      The Gaping Chasm.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 33010 3 33018
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     33019
Name     &OThe Gaping Chasm&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A massive crater in the desert floor. The hive structures of the
silithid tower above the sand like twisted, organic castles. Protectors
swarm from the tunnels to defend their queen.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    33018
Desc      The Noxious Lair.
~
