  Reset E 1 33008 10 11
Reset M 0 33010 2 33019
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     33020
Name     &ODunemaul Compound&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A crude camp built entirely of giant bones and stretched animal hides.
The Dunemaul ogres have claimed this southern corner of the desert,
smashing anything that enters their territory.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    33019
Desc      The Gaping Chasm.
~
