#ROOM
Vnum     33021
Name     &OThistleshrub Valley&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A deep, dry valley where aggressive, animated cacti and basilisks
roam. The heat here is magnified by the surrounding rock walls,
making it feel like an oven.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    33020
Desc      Dunemaul Compound.
~
