#ROOM
Vnum     33022
Name     &OEastmoon Ruins&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The twin city to Noonshade. These troll ruins are completely buried
in sand, with only the tops of the tallest pyramids visible. Ogres
frequently dig here, looking for shiny trinkets.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    33020
Desc      Dunemaul Compound.
~
#ENDEXIT
