#ROOM
Vnum     33023
Name     &bSouthbreak Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The southern edge of the continent. The Great Sea stretches endlessly
to the south, cold and unforgiving. The beach is littered with
strange, glowing kelp.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    33022
Desc      Eastmoon Ruins.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
