#ROOM
Vnum     33024
Name     &bLand's End Beach&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The southeastern tip of Tanaris. Giant sea turtles lay their eggs
in the warm sand here. It is one of the few peaceful spots in the
entire desert.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    33023
Desc      Southbreak Shore.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
