#ROOM
Vnum     33025
Name     &xNarain's Camp&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A bizarre camp filled with strange mechanical contraptions, scrying
orbs, and a crashed flying machine. Narain Soothfancy lives here in
self-imposed exile, trying to decode the secrets of the sands.
~
